# Grid Localization Service
# Estimates robot pose on the map using laser scan matching

# Request
# If scan is empty, the service will use the latest scan from the subscribed topic
sensor_msgs/LaserScan scan

---

# Response
bool success
string message
geometry_msgs/PoseWithCovarianceStamped pose
float64 confidence  # 0.0 to 1.0, higher is better
